author: Vickryah Ilma
text:
Righteous indignation.
Not a fan of violence,  but I got to say I respect a man who stands up for his wife.  He humiliated the man who humiliated her.  Fair play?  What do you all think?

author: Vickryah Ilma
text: Jada has a medical condition. Dan Chris membuat lolucon tentang hal itu yang tidak bisa ditertawakan. Lalu Will membela kehormatan istrinya. If I were on the jury, I'd say Will is "NOT GUILTY", defending his wife from verbal abuse, of something she, and others, are powerless. https://t.co/Q4jhtzG6E1
